01:02:32,770 --> 01:02:37,770
So when Nancy went into a
tailspin after Richard left her,

1179
01:02:37,840 --> 01:02:40,390
it was to Bill she turned.

1180
01:02:40,390 --> 01:02:44,057
He was the best friend
