01:03:48,822 --> 01:03:51,810
One of yours and Nancy's inventions.

1202
01:03:51,810 --> 01:03:53,899
This is her handwriting right here.

1203
01:03:53,899 --> 01:03:56,580
- Yeah.

1204
01:03:56,580 --> 01:03:58,980
- That puts the arsenic right
back into Nancy's hands.

1205
01:03:58,980 --> 01:04:01,995
Oh, and listen to this.

1206
01:04:01,995 --> 01:04:04,663
This is what we found in one of her notes.

