01:04:11,717 --> 01:04:15,747
"Bill was sent away, I was
repaired and almost forgotten.

1210
01:04:15,747 --> 01:04:18,637
"Richard tried to help
me, tried to save me

1211
01:04:18,637 --> 01:04:22,137
"with his sincere heart
and unending patience."

