01:05:05,271 --> 01:05:08,010
thought he was going to get,

1227
01:05:08,010 --> 01:05:10,330
about the first poison he ordered,

1228
01:05:10,330 --> 01:05:14,060
and the arsenic that
finally killed Nancy Lyon.

1229
01:05:14,060 --> 01:05:16,311
If you add it all up,
you will find that leads

1230
01:05:16,311 --> 01:05:19,619
a clear trail of damning
evidence from Nancy Lyon's

1231
01:05:19,619 --> 01:05:24,619
calculated murder to her
discontented husband Richard.

1232
01:05:26,168 --> 01:05:28,353
Everything else is irrelevant.

1233
01:05:36,240 --> 01:05:38,834
