1235
01:05:41,610 --> 01:05:45,090
life is not so simple as a
clear, well-marked trail.

1236
01:05:45,090 --> 01:05:47,220
Now as the prosecution points out,

1237
01:05:47,220 --> 01:05:51,831
this all began with a few
classic elements of murder,

1238
01:05:51,831 --> 01:05:55,160
a poisoned wife, an estranged husband

1239
01:05:55,160 --> 01:05:57,550
who appeared to have motive.

1240
01:05:57,550 --> 01:05:59,376
Now the prosecution will contend.

