01:07:41,781 --> 01:07:43,119
- Yes.

1276
01:07:43,119 --> 01:07:44,897
- [Jerri] And what was she signing?

1277
01:07:44,897 --> 01:07:47,966
- Well she changed her
life insurance beneficiary

